text: WTH is going on? It’s like GMB is the Wild West for small businesses and the shady sheriff (Google) is letting DoorDash take over delivery through theft and intimidation. DD operating as an oil baron drilling holes in everyone’s land as a test. It doesn’t cost the business anything but it’s jacking up the landscape. And what’s next?
